{"name":"Spell Countermeasures","permission":{"default":0,"zcRawgexeM2xX0kp":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You are targeted by a spell or in the area of a spell.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You quickly create a magical protection for yourself, tailored to a spell about to harm you. Against the triggering spell, you gain a +2 status bonus to AC and saving throws, and you gain resistance 5 against the spell’s damage.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> Increase the resistance by 2.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["abjuration"],"selected":{"abjuration":"Abjuration","custom":"Magus"},"rarity":{"value":"uncommon"},"custom":"Magus"},"rarity":{"value":"common"},"usage":{"value":"held-in-one-hand"},"rules":[],"level":{"value":3},"spellType":{"value":"focus"},"spellCategory":{"value":""},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"abj"},"components":{"value":"somatic"},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":""},"time":{"value":"reaction"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":"","applyMod":false},"damageType":{"value":""},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"save":{"basic":"","value":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"prepared":{"value":""},"location":{"value":"3JtdpPrgvStzkdiL"},"spellCategorie":{"value":"focus"},"primarycheck":{"value":""},"secondarycheck":{"value":""},"areasize":{"value":""},"secondarycasters":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"TNcKRL6HGabvILn5"}
{"name":"Magus Potency","permission":{"default":0,"zcRawgexeM2xX0kp":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>The target gains the benefit of a <em>+1 weapon potency</em> rune, granting a +1 item bonus to attack rolls with the targeted weapon or your unarmed attacks, if you targeted yourself. If cast on a weapon, this spell ends if you cease holding the weapon.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Heightened (3rd)</strong> The unarmed attacks or weapons are <em>+1 striking</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (4th)</strong> The unarmed attacks or weapons are <em>+2 striking</em>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (7th)</strong> The unarmed attacks or weapons are <em>+3 greater striking</em>.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["evocation"],"selected":{"evocation":"Evocation","custom":"Magus"},"rarity":{"value":"uncommon"},"custom":"Magus"},"rarity":{"value":"common"},"usage":{"value":"held-in-one-hand"},"rules":[],"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"focus"},"spellCategory":{"value":""},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"evo"},"components":{"value":"somatic"},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"you or one weapon you're wielding"},"range":{"value":"touch"},"area":{"value":""},"time":{"value":"1"},"duration":{"value":"1 minute"},"damage":{"value":"","applyMod":false},"damageType":{"value":""},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"save":{"basic":"","value":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"prepared":{"value":""},"location":{"value":"3JtdpPrgvStzkdiL"},"spellCategorie":{"value":"focus"},"primarycheck":{"value":""},"secondarycheck":{"value":""},"areasize":{"value":""},"secondarycasters":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"jCM13FfR7OP6R0wM"}
